(155, 1, '2016-09-14 11:59:55', '2016-09-14 01:59:55', 'Do you like wine?\r\nWe are proud to announce that you can include a 2 day Wine Tour into your itinerary for FREE.\r\nWe will cover the transportation, accommodation and meals for those 2 days.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-156" src="http://localhost/baodao/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/purple-grapes-553463-675x450.jpg" alt="purple-grapes-553463-675x450" width="675" height="450" />\r\n\r\nTo be honest, Japanese Wine is actually not that famous, YET. A major reason is the climate: That is because most of Japan is too humid and wet in summer. However, some areas in Hokkaido are ideal for growing vines, thanks to dry summers with low precipitation and ideal temperatures.\r\nMany wineries started growing wine in Hokkaido and are receiving more and more attention through increasing quality. Together with high quality local dairies and meats, we see a great potential of Hokkaido becoming internationally famous for wine.\r\nWe put together FREE TOURS focusing on Hokkaido wine. Visit the wineries, get to know how the wine is made and enjoy the region with its culinary specialties.\r\n\r\nWe have 4 options for you:\r\n<a href="http://hokkaido-sightseeing.com/en/sample/kami-furano/">Sep 22-23 Furano 2 Days</a>\r\n<a href="http://hokkaido-sightseeing.com/en/sample/enjoy-wine-in-otaru-free-tour/">Sep 26-27 Otaru 2 Days</a>\r\n<a href="http://hokkaido-sightseeing.com/en/sample/2411/">Oct 6-7 Hakodate 2 Days</a>\r\n<a href="http://hokkaido-sightseeing.com/en/sample/tokachi/">Oct 11-12 Tokachi 2 Days</a>\r\n\r\nAll options above are FREE Wine Tours, including accommodation, meals, transportation and activities such as vineyard visits and wine tasting\r\nCheck out our <a href="http://hokkaido-sightseeing.com/en/categories/wine-tours/">SPECIAL PAGE</a> for more details and inquire now!', 'Include a 2 Day Wine-Tour in your itinerary for FREE!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'include-a-2-day-wine-tour-in-your-itinerary-for-free', '', '', '2016-09-14 11:59:55', '2016-09-14 01:59:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baodao/?p=155', 0, 'post', '', 0),
