(158, 1, '2016-09-14 12:01:26', '2016-09-14 02:01:26', 'Lonely Planet made a list of Asia’s top recommended travel destinations to visit in the next 12 months, and guess which location came up on top?\r\nHokkaido, Japan!\r\nDefined as a “classic destination…, offering a fresh twist for travellers, regions packed full of action and edge-of-the-map places you’ve probably never heard of” (<a href="https://www.lonelyplanet.com/best-in-asia">Lonely-Planet.com</a>).\r\n\r\nMany people think of Hokkaido as a winter escape paradise, but Lonely Planet warns readers “DON’T BE SNOW-BLIND TO HOKKAIDO’S YEAR-ROUND CHARMS.”\r\n\r\nThat’s exactly why we offer monthly tours all-year-round on the island of Hokkaido, full of outdoor adventure, tempting seafood, and breathtaking sights Mother Nature is proud to share. We’ve known of these off-beaten charms for years, and we want to share that with you too! Be the first to start this new adventure by checking out our custom tours online today!<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-159" src="http://localhost/baodao/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/placeholder_image.png" alt="placeholder_image" width="1080" height="625" />', 'Hokkaido Chosen as #1 by Lonely Planet for “Best-in-Asia” Travel Destination!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hokkaido-chosen-as-1-by-lonely-planet-for-best-in-asia-travel-destination', '', '', '2016-09-14 12:01:26', '2016-09-14 02:01:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baodao/?p=158', 0, 'post', '', 0),
