(165, 1, '2016-09-14 12:12:29', '2016-09-14 02:12:29', '<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-166" src="http://localhost/baodao/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/DSC_0879-e1465181182953.jpg" alt="dsc_0879-e1465181182953" width="980" height="616" />\r\n\r\nThank you for visiting our new website, and for stopping by to read our new blog! We are very excited to share the best Hokkaido has to offer.\r\n\r\nOn this blog, our staff at Hokkaido Treasure Island Travel will personally write a message to our visitors and everyone interested in Hokkaido, with a very local perspective on the island. We don’t just plan the trips we offer without going to experience it ourselves; we try each activity and visit each location to make sure it’s the best plan for your travels. With this blog, we will share what we have experienced too! We hope to keep you updated with the latest information and fun activities to enjoy on Hokkaido.\r\n\r\nWarning: You may come to Hokkaido sooner than you think after reading what we have to share!!\r\n\r\nLet us know with a quick e-mail if you have any questions or requests for new sample itineraries. Comments are always welcome; we love to hear from Hokkaido fans!\r\n\r\nWe look forward to your visit to the treasure island of Hokkaido!\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\nYour Hokkaido Treasure Island Travel Team', 'Welcome to our Blog!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'welcome-to-our-blog', '', '', '2016-09-14 12:12:29', '2016-09-14 02:12:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baodao/?p=165', 0, 'post', '', 0),
