(363, 1, '2016-11-07 11:58:39', '2016-11-07 00:58:39', 'I just wanted to give you a big thank you Hitomi. Our second visit to Hokkaido was a much more enjoyable and memorable one.\r\n\r\nSo impressed with your swift response, thoughtfulness and kindness that you showed from our pre arrival emails till the end of our trip.\r\nMy daughter would also like to thank you for arranging vegan meals for her throughout the trip. The meals were superb.\r\n\r\nAnother big thank you to Mr. Endo, our driver. He was awesome. We felt safe and comfortable to have him traveling with us.\r\n\r\nYou asked me which places I liked most. What came into my mind is not any places but every people we had met during our trip.\r\nThe people at Murase Farm, the cycling guide, the nature guide of Shiretoko 5 Lakes trekking, the canoeing guide at Kushiro Wetland National Park and the soba master. All are great and loving people.\r\n\r\nThank you again for making our second visit in Hokkaido so memorable!\r\n\r\nI will definitely recommend Hokkaido Treasure Island Travel Inc. to all my friends who will be visiting Hokkaido.\r\n\r\nShirley\r\n<div>\r\n<p class="locate">Shirley(United Kingdom)</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<p class="locate"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-100" src="http://localhost/baodao/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/160828-1-330x330-300x300.jpg" alt="160828-1-330x330" width="300" height="300" /> <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-101" src="http://localhost/baodao/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/160828-2-330x330-300x300.jpg" alt="160828-2-330x330" width="300" height="300" /> <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-102" src="http://localhost/baodao/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/160828-3-330x330-300x300.jpg" alt="160828-3-330x330" width="300" height="300" /> <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-103" src="http://localhost/baodao/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/160828-4-330x330-300x300.jpg" alt="160828-4-330x330" width="300" height="300" /></p>', 'What came into my mind is not any places but every people we had met during our trip.', 'Shirley(United Kingdom)', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '99-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-07 11:58:39', '2016-11-07 00:58:39', '', 99, 'http://localhost/baodao/99-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
